examples.en: She risked her life to save her children.
He was a man of principle and risked talk.
She risked a glance back over her shoulder.
He risked his life helping others to escape.
We risked losing a lot of money in this venture
He risked $50 on the horse race and lost it all.
He risked all his money on starting his own business.
Lurie risked a pretty big chunk of change on the race.
Two firefighters risked their lives to save the children.
Workers who broke the strike risked being attacked when they left the factory.
He has risked life and limb (=has done very dangerous things) to photograph some of the world's most dangerous animals.
